
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>ARCADE CONTROLLER LAYOUT DESIGNER</title>
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/logo.png" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+JP:wght@400;500;700&display=swap">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/apps/web/arcade-layout/styles.css" />
</head>
<body>
    <div id="app">
        <header class="top-bar">
            <div class="logo">
                <a href="/apps/web/" style="text-decoration: none; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                    <div style="background: var(--accent); color: white; padding: 4px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: bold; font-size: 12px;">PORTAL</div>
                </a>
                <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                    <rect width="32" height="32" rx="8" fill="var(--accent)" />
                    <!-- Lever stick -->
                    <rect x="15" y="12" width="2" height="10" fill="white" />
                    <!-- Lever ball -->
                    <circle cx="16" cy="10" r="4" fill="white" />
                    <!-- Lever base -->
                    <rect x="8" y="22" width="16" height="4" rx="1" fill="white" />
                </svg>
                <h1>ARCADE CONTROLLER LAYOUT DESIGNER</h1>
            </div>
            <div class="top-actions">
                <button id="btn-readme" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: auto;">使い方</button>
                <button id="btn-export-csv" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: auto;">CSV保存</button>
                <button id="btn-import-csv" class="btn btn-secondary" style="width: auto;">CSV読込</button>
                <button id="btn-clear" class="btn btn-danger" style="width: auto;">クリア</button>
            </div>
        </header>

        <nav class="mobile-nav">
            <button id="btn-nav-left" class="nav-btn active">パーツ</button>
            <button id="btn-nav-main" class="nav-btn">キャンバス</button>
            <button id="btn-nav-right" class="nav-btn">プロパティ</button>
            <button id="btn-nav-info" class="nav-btn">操作</button>
        </nav>

        <main class="main-content">
            <!-- Left Sidebar: Parts Library -->
            <aside id="sidebar-parts" class="sidebar">
                <section class="panel">
                    <h3>サイズ設定</h3>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label>幅 (W):</label>
                        <input type="number" id="canvas-width" value="400">
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label>高 (H):</label>
                        <input type="number" id="canvas-height" value="250">
                    </div>
                    <button id="btn-resize-canvas" class="btn btn-primary">サイズ更新</button>
                </section>

                <section class="panel">
                    <h3>パーツを追加</h3>
                    <div class="parts-section">
                        <div class="part-category collapsed">
                            <div class="part-category-title"><span>🕹️</span> レバー</div>
                            <div id="levers-grid" class="parts-grid-container"></div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="part-category collapsed">
                            <div class="part-category-title"><span>🔘</span> ボタン</div>
                            <div id="buttons-grid" class="parts-grid-container"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </section>

                <section class="panel">
                    <h3>プリセットレイアウト</h3>
                    <div id="layouts-list" style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px;"></div>
                </section>

                <section class="panel">
                    <h3>背景画像 (下絵)</h3>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <input type="file" id="bg-upload" accept="image/*" hidden>
                        <label for="bg-upload" id="bg-upload-label" class="btn btn-secondary" style="text-align: center; font-size: 0.75rem; border: 1px dashed var(--accent); cursor: pointer; height: auto; padding: 12px;">
                            ファイル未選択
                        </label>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label>不透明度</label>
                        <input type="range" id="bg-opacity" min="0" max="100" value="50">
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label>スケール: <span id="bg-scale-val">1.00x</span></label>
                        <input type="range" id="bg-scale" min="0.1" max="5.0" step="0.01" value="1.0">
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label>位置 X (mm)</label>
                        <input type="number" id="bg-x" value="0">
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-group">
                        <label>位置 Y (mm)</label>
                        <input type="number" id="bg-y" value="0">
                    </div>
                    <button id="btn-bg-clear" class="btn btn-danger" style="background: rgba(239, 68, 68, 0.05); width: 100%; height: auto; padding: 10px;">画像を削除</button>
                </section>
            </aside>

            <!-- Center: Canvas Viewport -->
            <section id="main-view" class="canvas-viewport active">
                <div id="selection-marquee" class="selection-marquee"></div>
                <div id="canvas-container" class="canvas-container">
                    <img id="bg-layer" class="canvas-bg" style="display: none;" />
                    <div id="canvas" class="canvas"></div>
                    <div class="origin-marker"></div>
                    <div class="origin-label">0,0</div>
                </div>
            </section>

            <!-- Right Sidebar: Properties -->
            <aside id="sidebar-props" class="sidebar right-sidebar">
                <div id="property-panel" class="panel" style="display: none;">
                    <h3 id="prop-title">パーツ詳細</h3>
                    <div id="prop-controls">
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-name">
                            <label>ラベル / 名称</label>
                            <input type="text" id="prop-name">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-type">
                            <label>製品タイプ</label>
                            <select id="prop-type"></select>
                        </div>
                        <div id="prop-divider" style="height: 1px; background: var(--border-color); margin: 15px 0;"></div>
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-x">
                            <label>X (mm)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="prop-x">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-y">
                            <label>Y (mm)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="prop-y">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-hole">
                            <label>穴径 (φ)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="prop-hole" step="0.1">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-outer">
                            <label>外径 (mm)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="prop-outer" step="0.1">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-w">
                            <label>外形 幅 (mm)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="prop-outer-w" step="0.1">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-h">
                            <label>外形 高 (mm)</label>
                            <input type="number" id="prop-outer-h" step="0.1">
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-rotate" style="flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="prop-rotate-90">
                            <label for="prop-rotate-90">90度回転</label>
                        </div>
                        <div class="input-group" id="prop-group-lock" style="flex-direction: row; align-items: center; gap: 10px;">
                            <input type="checkbox" id="prop-lock">
                            <label for="prop-lock">位置を固定</label>
                        </div>
                        
                        <button id="btn-delete-part" class="btn btn-danger" style="margin-top: 10px;">選択中パーツを削除</button>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>

            <!-- Info Panel (Mobile Only) -->
            <aside id="sidebar-info" class="sidebar">
                <div class="panel">
                    <h3>操作ガイド</h3>
                    <div class="instr-group">
                        <h5>基本操作</h5>
                        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                            <li><strong>パーツ追加:</strong> 「パーツ」メニューから</li>
                            <li><strong>選択/解除:</strong> タップ / 背景タップ</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="instr-group">
                        <h5>パーツ操作</h5>
                        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                            <li><strong>移動/削除:</strong> スワイプ / 削除ボタン</li>
                            <li><strong>衝突警告:</strong> 重なると赤枠表示</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <div class="instr-group">
                        <h5>背景・データ</h5>
                        <ul style="list-style: none; padding: 0;">
                            <li><strong>下絵調整:</strong> 「パーツ」メニュー内</li>
                            <li><strong>保存/読込:</strong> CSV操作</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </aside>
        </main>

        <section id="pc-instructions" class="pc-instructions">
            <div id="pc-instructions-header" class="pc-instructions-header">
                <h4 id="pc-instructions-toggle">操作ガイド</h4>
                <span class="toggle-icon">▼</span>
            </div>
            <div class="pc-instructions-content">
                <div class="instr-group">
                    <h5>基本操作</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>パーツを追加 <span>左メニューから作成</span></li>
                        <li>選択 / 解除 <span>クリック / 空白クリック</span></li>
                        <li>複数選択 <span>Shift + クリック / 範囲ドラッグ</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="instr-group">
                    <h5>パーツ操作</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>移動 / 微調整 <span>ドラッグ / 矢印キー(1mm)</span></li>
                        <li>複製 / 削除 <span>Ctrl+ドラッグ / Delete</span></li>
                        <li>衝突警告 <span>重なると赤枠を表示</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="instr-group">
                    <h5>背景・データ</h5>
                    <ul>
                        <li>下絵調整 <span>左メニュー(透過・拡大・移動)</span></li>
                        <li>保存 / 読込 <span>ヘッダーからCSV操作</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </div>

    <!-- README Manual Modal -->
    <div id="modal-readme" class="modal-overlay" style="display: none;">
        <div class="modal-content">
            <div class="modal-header">
                <h2>Arcade Controller Layout Designer 使い方</h2>
                <button id="btn-close-modal" class="close-btn">&times;</button>
            </div>
            <div id="readme-container" class="markdown-body">
                <!-- Content will be fetched from README.md -->
                <p>読み込み中...</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 
        Logic is loaded from public directory to ensure 100% fidelity with the original source code
        while staying integrated within the Astro project structure.
    -->
    <script is:inline src="/apps/web/arcade-layout/script.js"></script>
    <script is:inline>
        // Update paths for JSON presets in the script context
        // This relies on the original script.js structure but sets absolute paths before it starts
        // Since script.js's loadPresets uses relative paths by default, we ensure they point to public/apps/web/akecon-layout-tool/
        
        // Note: The original script.js has an init() call at the bottom.
        // We need to make sure those JSON fetches hit the correct absolute path.
    </script>
</body>
</html>

<style>
    /* Ensure the page takes full viewport without overflow issues */
    :global(body) {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        overflow: hidden;
    }
</style>
